              <p>Intuitive mobile app for fitness tracking</p>
              <div class="portfolio-tags">
                <span>React Native</span>
                <span>UI/UX</span>
                <span>Firebase</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-item fade-in">
        <div class="portfolio-image">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/590016/pexels-photo-590016.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="SaaS Dashboard" />
          <div class="portfolio-overlay">
            <div class="portfolio-info">
              <h4>SaaS Dashboard</h4>
