                <span>Python</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-item fade-in">
        <div class="portfolio-image">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1779487/pexels-photo-1779487.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Restaurant Website" />
          <div class="portfolio-overlay">
            <div class="portfolio-info">
              <h4>Restaurant Website</h4>
              <p>Beautiful restaurant site with online ordering</p>
              <div class="portfolio-tags">
                <span>WordPress</span>
                <span>WooCommerce</span>
                <span>PHP</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-item fade-in">
        <div class="portfolio-image">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/574077/pexels-photo-574077.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Brand Identity" />
          <div class="portfolio-overlay">
            <div class="portfolio-info">
              <h4>Brand Identity</h4>
              <p>Complete brand redesign and guidelines</p>
              <div class="portfolio-tags">
                <span>Logo Design</span>
